        <mxCell id="14" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="ExtractThirdIds(...)&#xa;&#xa;Input scheme&#xa;thirdPartyLinks: ProcessThirdPartyLinksResponse | null&#xa;&#xa;For each content item&#xa;1. Find first link where rel == &quot;third&quot;&#xa;2. Read href&#xa;3. Trim trailing slash&#xa;4. Take last path segment&#xa;&#xa;Output scheme&#xa;IReadOnlyList&lt;string&gt;&#xa;[ thirdId1, thirdId2, ... ]" vertex="1">
