        <mxCell id="21" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" value="Important notes&#xa;&#xa;- This endpoint treats process_id as a Gestiona file id. It does not resolve from process_number.&#xa;- The upstream thirdparty object id is not returned. The returned id comes from the rel=&quot;third&quot; href.&#xa;- Missing rel=&quot;third&quot; links are skipped.&#xa;- Empty content returns success with an empty thirds string.&#xa;- The response envelope is GatewayResponse." vertex="1">
